---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about Christmas Logistics LLC - a locally-owned Amazon Delivery Service Partner proudly serving Denver, Colorado since 2021.">
  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-badge">Our Story</span>
      <h1>About Christmas Logistics</h1>
      <p>Your trusted local delivery partner in Denver, Colorado.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="section story">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-grid">
        <div class="story-content">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>
            Christmas Logistics was founded in 2021 with a simple mission: deliver packages
            with the same care and reliability you'd expect from a neighbor. What started
            as a small operation has grown into a team of 85+ dedicated professionals
            serving the Denver metro area.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our founder saw an opportunity to combine enterprise-level logistics capabilities
            with the personal touch of a local business. As an Amazon Delivery Service Partner,
            we have access to world-class technology and training while maintaining the
            flexibility to truly serve our community.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, we've delivered over 500,000 packages to homes and businesses across Denver.
            But more importantly, we've built a team that feels like family‚Äîdrivers who take
            pride in their work and genuinely care about the customers they serve.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-visual">
          <div class="story-stats">
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">2021</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Founded</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">85+</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Team Members</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">500K+</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Packages Delivered</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <span class="stat-number">40+</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Vehicles</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="section mission">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission-content">
        <div class="mission-box">
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>
            To deliver every package safely, on time, and with care‚Äîwhile creating
            meaningful career opportunities for members of our Denver community.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-box">
          <h3>Our Vision</h3>
          <p>
            To be Denver's most trusted delivery partner, known for excellence in
            service and as a workplace where people build lasting careers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="section values">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
        <p>The values that guide everything we do.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
          <h3>Safety</h3>
          <p>We never compromise on safety. Every driver, every delivery, every day. Our team goes home safe, and your packages arrive intact.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">‚è∞</div>
          <h3>Reliability</h3>
          <p>We do what we say. Customers and partners count on our consistency. When we commit to a delivery, we deliver.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">üë•</div>
          <h3>Teamwork</h3>
          <p>We succeed together. Every team member matters, from drivers to dispatchers. We support each other and celebrate wins together.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">‚≠ê</div>
          <h3>Excellence</h3>
          <p>We strive to exceed expectations in every delivery. Good enough isn't good enough‚Äîwe aim for exceptional service.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">üíö</div>
          <h3>Integrity</h3>
          <p>We operate with honesty and transparency in everything we do. Trust is earned through consistent, ethical actions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">üèòÔ∏è</div>
          <h3>Community</h3>
          <p>We're proud to serve our neighbors. Our drivers live in the communities they deliver to‚Äîit's personal for us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Amazon Partnership Section -->
  <section class="section partnership">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="partnership-content">
        <div class="partnership-text">
          <h2>Proud Amazon Delivery Service Partner</h2>
          <p>
            As an Amazon DSP, Christmas Logistics operates with the support of one of the
            world's most advanced logistics networks. Our drivers receive comprehensive
            training, access to cutting-edge delivery technology, and vehicles equipped
            with the latest safety features.
          </p>
          <p>
            But we're more than just a number in a network. We're a locally-owned business
            that combines Amazon's enterprise-level standards with the flexibility and care
            of a small company. You get the best of both worlds: reliable, professional
            service with a personal touch.
          </p>
          <div class="partnership-benefits">
            <div class="benefit">
              <span class="check">‚úì</span>
              <span>Amazon-certified training programs</span>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit">
              <span class="check">‚úì</span>
              <span>Modern, well-maintained vehicle fleet</span>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit">
              <span class="check">‚úì</span>
              <span>Advanced routing and tracking technology</span>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit">
              <span class="check">‚úì</span>
              <span>Local ownership and management</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <div class="cta-text">
          <h2>Join Our Growing Team</h2>
          <p>We're always looking for reliable, motivated people to join the Christmas Logistics family.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/careers" class="btn btn-gold">View Open Positions</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--christmas-green) 0%, #0d3d24 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-hero p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Story Section */
  .story {
    background: var(--snow-white);
  }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .story-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .story-content p {
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .story-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--christmas-green);
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--christmas-green);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
  }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission {
    background: white;
  }

  .mission-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .mission-box {
    background: var(--frost);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--christmas-green);
  }

  .mission-box h3 {
    color: var(--christmas-green);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .mission-box p {
    color: #555;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Values Section */
  .values {
    background: var(--frost);
  }

  .value-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    color: var(--christmas-green);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Partnership Section */
  .partnership {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--christmas-green) 0%, #0d3d24 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .partnership-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .partnership-text h2 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .partnership-text p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .partnership-benefits {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .benefit {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .check {
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--midnight) 0%, var(--charcoal) 100%);
  }

  .cta-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .cta h2 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .cta p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .story-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .mission-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .partnership-benefits {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .story-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
